    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "texts": [
        {
          "plain_text": "The first time you drive a stick shift and you truly feel connected to the machine. The countless times you enter the zone with true focus while you work. The intense emotions of love. The first time you build your own keyboard. The first time you achieve success. The camaraderie of your team.",
          "annotations": {
            "bold": false,
            "italic": false,
